o Mizuki, nơi anh gặp một đứa trẻ tên là Umi. Anh ấy rất ngạc nhiên khi biết Umi là con gái của Mizuki Nagumo. Mẹ của Nagumo Mizuki nói chuyện với anh và nói với anh rằng Umi là con gái của ông.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"256299","season":1,"vote_average":7.7,"vote_count":6},"modified":"2024-12-21T11:14:29.000Z","cast":["Mục Hắc Liên","Izutani Rana","Arimura Kasumi","Shinobu Otake","Kotone Furukawa","Sosuke Ikematsu","Taisei Kido","Go Riju","Yasufumi Hayashi","Naomi Nishida","Ren Sudo","Kyoka","Ayumu Nakajima","Maho Yamada"],"director":["Hiroki Kazama","Mai Takano"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Mục Hắc Liên","name_vi":"Mục Hắc Liên","name_original":"Ren Meguro","tmdb_id":3190917,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tlGzRInzO6ItiezXoWvF3XYrQ0X.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3190917"},{"name":"Izutani Rana","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Izutani Rana","tmdb_id":4294998,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p0N3Ju6klHyXNgRnekslgADH6Mk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4294998"},{"name":"Arimura Kasumi","name_vi":"Arimura Kasumi","name_original":"Kasumi Arimura","tmdb_id":1039305,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wgRmACLMYhZWmMOaGUmUUMYPDTG.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1039305"},{"name":"Shinobu Otake","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Shinobu Otake","tmdb_id":545825,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/az5hCPy37MFM9EH2f3gn1cTBhA6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/545825"},{"name":"Kotone Furukawa","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kotone Furukawa","tmdb_id":2187869,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vcW4qq52yAWuIwKlHw3s5y2HEnI.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2187869"},{"name":"Sosuke Ikematsu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Sosuke Ikematsu","tmdb_id":1116510,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mNhgUAKfHdKQXhbhbAhKcRUHy30.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1116510"},{"name":"Taisei Kido","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Taisei